Relatórios gerados pelo Maven

Este documento contém uma visão geral dos vários relatórios que são automaticamente gerados por Maven . Cada relatório está descrito abaixo

Visão Geral

Documento Descrição
Javadoc Javadoc API documentation.
Test Javadoc Test Javadoc API documentation.
Source Xref HTML based, cross-reference version of Java source code.
Test Source Xref HTML based, cross-reference version of Java test source code.
Surefire Report Report on the test results of the project.
Clover Report on test coverage
Checkstyle Relatório do estilo de convenção de codificação.
PMD Verificação das regras de codificação.
FindBugs Gera um relatório do código fonte utilizando o FindBugs.
OWASP dependency check Generates an aggregate report of all child Maven projects providing details on any published vulnerabilities within project dependencies. This report is a best effort and may contain false positives and false negatives.
JDepend JDepend traverses Java class file directories and generates design quality metrics for each Java package. JDepend allows you to automatically measure the quality of a design in terms of its extensibility, reusability, and maintainability to manage package dependencies effectively.
Dependency Updates Report Provides details of the dependencies which have updated versions available.
Plugin Updates Report Provides details of the plugins used by this project which have newer versions available.
